{"tid":1998620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有冇連登仔夠膽挑戰？ ]鬼佬禁足居家 玩洋腸頂洗頭水挑戰！","createTime":"2020-05-02T13:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:48:30.000Z","uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"37c73e86df6489d39faf0c05382b86ceaaa188e2","tid":1998620,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"前年連登仔笑港女冇波 平<br />\n玩唔撚到心形胸challenge<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QnOP9Sk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQnOP9Sk.jpg&h=735ed5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oHdR6h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oHdR6h.png&h=ac8999b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS16sED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS16sED.png&h=80fcfaba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jeCNb6k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjeCNb6k.png&h=a36e0628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知今次連登仔又做唔做到國際標準玩洋腸Shampochallenge？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5ykw43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5ykw43.png&h=ca8346f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">\n事緣係外國網持續居家令，留喺屋企隔離個幾兩個月玩到冇嘢好玩，玩到要玩J！喺Twitter興起左腸腸挑戰#shampoochallenge，顧名思義就係用洋腸頂住支shampoo，唔跌先係挑戰成功！\n</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n連登個個講到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />30cm 唔會連支洗頭水都頂唔到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_rBb7Blx-Z/?igshid=1ns8tz033mmq6[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https